WEBVTT

01:40.500 --> 01:45.930
[Speed and Love]

01:46.220 --> 01:48.750
[Episode 7]

02:07.630 --> 02:10.139
Where's the keychain Sanlai mentioned?

02:34.390 --> 02:35.230
Come and eat.

02:37.910 --> 02:40.520
Could it be that Jin Zhao has it on him?

03:01.870 --> 03:02.910
Drink your milk.

03:04.290 --> 03:05.680
I don't like milk.

03:05.870 --> 03:06.820
Then eat the egg.

03:07.730 --> 03:09.210
I like eggs even less.

03:11.670 --> 03:13.460
If you don't eat, go back to Jin Qiang's.

03:13.460 --> 03:14.180
Fine.

03:14.390 --> 03:16.200
I'll eat, okay?

03:19.750 --> 03:21.710
You're even stricter than my mom.

03:24.980 --> 03:25.930
I signed my name.

03:29.400 --> 03:30.750
What you signed was a hospital form,

03:30.750 --> 03:32.710
not a life contract.

03:33.290 --> 03:35.880
If you became malnourished
while staying with me,

03:35.880 --> 03:37.280
what would people think?

03:39.690 --> 03:40.750
Finish the fruit too.

03:40.750 --> 03:41.630
That's a lot.

03:42.100 --> 03:44.100
Do you want to go back to Jin Qiang's?

04:35.810 --> 04:37.010
Mr. Lin, you're here.

04:37.720 --> 04:38.600
Who are you?

04:39.070 --> 04:39.930
Don't touch me.

04:41.180 --> 04:42.300
What are you...

04:42.840 --> 04:44.240
Why did you get physical?

04:44.280 --> 04:45.480
What's going on here?

04:45.840 --> 04:46.520
Miss.

04:47.400 --> 04:48.250
Miss Wan.

04:48.570 --> 04:50.159
A few days ago,
your people came to my house

04:50.159 --> 04:51.750
and tried to kidnap my sister.

04:51.750 --> 04:52.750
For this matter,

04:53.040 --> 04:55.280
you owe me an explanation.

04:55.370 --> 04:56.250
My people

04:56.780 --> 04:57.980
kidnapped my friend?

04:58.080 --> 04:59.270
You must have misunderstood.

04:59.270 --> 05:00.150
Ask him.

05:01.520 --> 05:03.680
Mr. Lin, I didn't mean to kidnap her.

05:03.700 --> 05:05.310
I... I was just messing around with her.

05:05.310 --> 05:05.750
It's true.

05:05.750 --> 05:06.950
I was messing around.

05:07.370 --> 05:08.750
I'm just messing around too.

05:08.750 --> 05:09.750
Let go.

05:10.050 --> 05:10.690
It hurts.

05:11.930 --> 05:12.450
Let go.

05:12.770 --> 05:14.100
You've already hit him.

05:14.650 --> 05:15.850
What more do you want?

05:19.170 --> 05:20.950
If you want to be friends with my sister,

05:20.950 --> 05:21.680
that's fine.

05:22.040 --> 05:23.440
But you need to be polite.

05:24.140 --> 05:25.580
If she doesn't want to,

05:26.000 --> 05:27.170
then back off.

05:32.140 --> 05:33.460
Try that again,

05:34.750 --> 05:36.140
and you'll regret it.

05:41.380 --> 05:42.220
Hey, Lin,

05:42.380 --> 05:43.500
what do you mean?

06:04.440 --> 06:05.440
Have you decided?

06:05.700 --> 06:07.360
You're staying here to study?

06:08.430 --> 06:09.310
But

06:09.400 --> 06:10.190
I need to find

06:10.190 --> 06:12.140
a legitimate reason to stay here.

06:12.700 --> 06:14.650
Since my mom insists I go abroad,

06:14.900 --> 06:16.550
going to Canada or staying here

06:16.550 --> 06:17.700
is the same.

06:17.820 --> 06:19.220
Comparatively speaking,

06:19.220 --> 06:20.630
I prefer your country.

06:20.710 --> 06:21.970
It's warm and diverse.

06:22.220 --> 06:23.430
That's great, Mu.

06:23.590 --> 06:25.990
Which university
are you going to apply to?

06:28.040 --> 06:29.300
I haven't decided yet.

06:29.460 --> 06:31.110
I'm not good at languages.

06:31.260 --> 06:34.260
I might need to sign up
for a language foundation course first.

06:34.260 --> 06:35.140
What a coincidence!

06:35.140 --> 06:37.740
My family runs
a language training institute.

06:37.950 --> 06:40.220
We specialize
in less commonly taught languages.

06:40.220 --> 06:40.950
Really?

06:41.470 --> 06:43.390
Would you like to sign up
for my family's courses?

06:43.390 --> 06:44.650
I can go and take a look.

06:48.430 --> 06:49.110
This way.

06:51.730 --> 06:52.630
This is the language training school

06:52.630 --> 06:53.820
I told you about.

06:54.340 --> 06:55.070
It's so big.

06:55.090 --> 06:56.700
Of course. My family owns it.

06:56.790 --> 06:58.370
Let's go. I'll help you enroll.

06:58.370 --> 06:59.340
That's great.

07:01.200 --> 07:02.150
[Student Affairs Office]

07:05.930 --> 07:07.080
Welcome to join us.

07:07.400 --> 07:09.130
See you in class in a few days.

07:13.620 --> 07:14.090
Mu.

07:14.150 --> 07:15.000
Thank you.

07:15.450 --> 07:16.700
You already have some language foundation,

07:16.700 --> 07:18.140
so I enrolled you
in an intermediate class.

07:18.140 --> 07:19.600
This class, which is medium-sized,

07:19.600 --> 07:21.550
mainly consists of Chinese, foreigners,

07:21.550 --> 07:22.070
and Chinese nationals

07:22.070 --> 07:23.930
who are studying abroad like you.

07:24.090 --> 07:24.890
Come this way.

07:26.430 --> 07:27.340
But listen,

07:27.430 --> 07:28.910
to master a language,

07:29.140 --> 07:30.630
besides taking the foundation course,

07:30.630 --> 07:32.159
the most important thing is

07:32.320 --> 07:33.780
to communicate frequently

07:33.780 --> 07:35.240
with local people like us.

07:35.630 --> 07:36.890
But you always speak Chinese.

07:36.890 --> 07:38.870
I've never heard you speak
the local language.

07:38.870 --> 07:40.550
Don't worry.

07:40.580 --> 07:42.070
Don't overthink it.

07:42.950 --> 07:43.950
What do they mean?

07:44.340 --> 07:47.110
Don't worry. Don't overthink it.

07:47.900 --> 07:48.870
Don't worry.

07:48.940 --> 07:50.040
Don't worry.

07:50.070 --> 07:51.470
Come on, repeat after me.

07:51.590 --> 07:53.270
Don't worry.

07:53.880 --> 07:55.710
Don't wo-

07:56.260 --> 07:58.220
-rry.

07:58.470 --> 08:00.460
Don't overthink it. Lift your tone.

08:00.460 --> 08:02.330
Don't overthink it.

08:02.670 --> 08:04.320
Right. Now say them all together.

08:04.320 --> 08:07.920
Don't worry. Don't overthink it.

08:07.950 --> 08:09.430
Very good!

08:09.920 --> 08:10.700
I can speak it too.

08:10.700 --> 08:11.310
Go ahead.

08:11.870 --> 08:12.900
So beautiful.

08:13.430 --> 08:14.990
So beautiful.

08:15.110 --> 08:16.260
Thank you.

08:16.280 --> 08:17.430
Right. Thank you.

08:17.460 --> 08:18.060
What else?

08:18.110 --> 08:18.950
Also...

08:19.280 --> 08:21.840
Gently, gently.

08:21.870 --> 08:23.580
You get massages quite often, don't you?

08:23.580 --> 08:24.340
What else?

08:24.630 --> 08:25.220
Kiss.

08:25.340 --> 08:26.410
-Kiss?
-Kiss.

08:26.900 --> 08:29.020
-Kiss. Kiss.
-Kiss.

08:33.669 --> 08:35.330
It’s almost time for the race.

08:35.630 --> 08:36.960
Is your car ready?

08:38.020 --> 08:40.020
It still needs two important parts.

08:40.030 --> 08:41.390
I can't find them anywhere in the city.

08:41.390 --> 08:43.250
You're probably being targeted.

08:43.669 --> 08:45.070
You have to tough it out this time.

08:45.070 --> 08:46.190
I have confidence.

08:46.910 --> 08:48.340
This race is crucial.

08:48.500 --> 08:49.700
If you're placed in the top 3,

08:49.700 --> 08:51.700
you'll get into the top 10 by points.

09:10.700 --> 09:11.760
The door is closed.

09:12.220 --> 09:14.310
Doesn't he know you're coming back today?

09:14.310 --> 09:16.110
He definitely did it on purpose.

09:16.460 --> 09:18.460
He just doesn't want me to live here.

09:18.480 --> 09:19.510
This guy

09:19.820 --> 09:21.950
doesn't know how to treat a lady at all.

09:22.170 --> 09:23.170
Exactly.

09:24.820 --> 09:26.480
Why don't you stay at my place?

09:26.830 --> 09:28.470
My mom would love you.

09:31.640 --> 09:32.700
Never mind, Nana.

09:32.740 --> 09:34.580
I'd better go back to my dad's place.

09:34.580 --> 09:36.190
I need him to talk with my mom

09:36.190 --> 09:37.740
about follow-up.

09:38.350 --> 09:40.000
Alright. I'll take you there.

09:40.000 --> 09:41.000
Thanks, Nana.

09:56.700 --> 09:57.420
Dad?

09:57.650 --> 09:58.900
Dad, open the door!

10:43.190 --> 10:44.620
You stepped on my hand.

10:44.620 --> 10:46.580
I didn't even cry out in pain.

10:46.770 --> 10:48.260
Why did you shout?

10:48.380 --> 10:49.070
Dad?

10:50.600 --> 10:52.720
Dad, it's really you.

10:53.390 --> 10:54.850
Why are you sleeping here?

10:55.390 --> 10:57.820
It's nice here. It's cool.

11:01.990 --> 11:03.720
Why did you drink so much again?

11:03.960 --> 11:04.740
Let's go.

11:04.740 --> 11:06.540
Let's go home. Don't sleep here.

11:06.580 --> 11:08.500
The electrical circuit at home
is burned out.

11:08.500 --> 11:09.700
There's no electricity.

11:09.700 --> 11:11.690
The air conditioner is not working.

11:11.690 --> 11:13.030
Why don't you fix it?

11:13.170 --> 11:14.770
I can't be bothered to fix it.

11:17.380 --> 11:19.070
You can ask Jin Zhao to fix it.

11:19.550 --> 11:21.030
Let's go. Don't sleep here.

11:21.030 --> 11:23.170
This place has too many mosquitoes
and is not safe.

11:23.170 --> 11:24.290
Get up.

11:24.790 --> 11:26.100
Get up.

11:33.600 --> 11:35.400
Mrs. Zhao, where did you go?

11:35.660 --> 11:37.220
I took Xin to the countryside.

11:37.220 --> 11:38.240
We're going back tomorrow.

11:38.240 --> 11:39.040
What's wrong?

11:39.160 --> 11:40.620
You're going back to live?

11:41.130 --> 11:42.010
The key

11:42.120 --> 11:44.050
is under the flowerpot by the door.

11:44.140 --> 11:45.950
Open the door and let yourself in.

11:45.950 --> 11:48.220
No. My father fell asleep
next to garbage bins.

11:48.220 --> 11:50.350
I can't drag him away. What should I do?

11:50.540 --> 11:51.420
He did it again?

11:52.430 --> 11:53.310
Just ignore him.

11:53.310 --> 11:54.390
He sleeps everywhere.

11:54.390 --> 11:55.390
Just leave him be.

11:55.940 --> 11:57.050
No way.

11:57.100 --> 11:58.500
He... He can't sleep here.

11:58.500 --> 12:00.700
It's not safe,
and there are too many mosquitoes.

12:00.700 --> 12:02.190
Alright, leave him be.

12:02.380 --> 12:03.960
When he sobers up, he'll go home.

12:03.960 --> 12:05.750
Okay, I'll hang up now.

12:29.380 --> 12:30.760
Dad, wake up.

12:30.790 --> 12:32.220
Don't sleep here.

12:32.950 --> 12:33.740
Wake up.

12:33.990 --> 12:35.050
What are you doing?

12:39.710 --> 12:40.780
Where did you go?

12:42.110 --> 12:44.110
I went out to take care of something.

12:45.170 --> 12:46.210
Are you

12:46.570 --> 12:48.740
planning to let him sleep here tonight?

12:48.740 --> 12:50.420
You even made a careful preparation.

12:50.420 --> 12:51.740
What else could I do?

12:52.100 --> 12:53.500
Dad is completely drunk.

12:53.580 --> 12:55.070
I can't drag him away.

12:55.580 --> 12:56.620
If I don't cover him,

12:56.620 --> 12:58.420
he'll get bitten by mosquitoes.

13:01.160 --> 13:02.690
He's immune to mosquitoes.

13:04.170 --> 13:05.050
Let's go home.

13:10.250 --> 13:11.040
Be careful.

13:26.870 --> 13:28.230
Is Dad always like this?

13:28.370 --> 13:29.060
Yes.

13:30.090 --> 13:32.490
Why doesn't Mrs. Zhao
do anything about it?

13:32.620 --> 13:33.660
When he craves alcohol,

13:33.660 --> 13:34.620
he drinks himself unconscious.

13:34.620 --> 13:36.220
He sleeps wherever he drops.

13:37.400 --> 13:38.600
He's smart this time.

13:39.830 --> 13:40.540
Dad.

13:41.630 --> 13:43.630
How did he become like this?

13:47.850 --> 13:49.780
When he wakes up, ask him yourself.

13:55.410 --> 13:56.810
Why aren't the lights on?

13:58.330 --> 14:00.020
The electrical circuit is burned out.

14:00.020 --> 14:02.150
Dad said he can't be bothered to fix it.

14:02.870 --> 14:03.590
Wait.

14:05.950 --> 14:07.680
I just bought this flashlight.

14:12.840 --> 14:13.560
Here you go.

14:34.190 --> 14:35.380
Do you need my help?

15:12.880 --> 15:13.840
Is it fixed?

15:27.740 --> 15:29.290
Turn off the lights.

15:30.530 --> 15:33.450
I need to get some sleep.
Turn off the lights.

15:33.770 --> 15:34.900
You smell terrible.

15:35.210 --> 15:36.470
Come. Go take a shower.

15:41.020 --> 15:42.190
Get up.

15:44.650 --> 15:45.960
Mu.

15:47.500 --> 15:48.500
Zhao.

15:49.660 --> 15:51.440
My good children.

15:53.440 --> 15:54.370
I

15:54.680 --> 15:56.040
owe you an apology.

15:56.530 --> 15:58.700
I'm not a good father.

16:00.580 --> 16:02.710
You're drunk. Stop talking nonsense.

16:02.960 --> 16:05.030
I'm happy that Mu is here.

16:05.520 --> 16:06.900
Don't leave anymore.

16:06.930 --> 16:08.130
I'll take care of you.

16:09.070 --> 16:10.670
I'll buy you delicious food.

16:10.820 --> 16:11.860
I'll cook for you.

16:25.570 --> 16:26.940
After drinking coffee this late,

16:26.940 --> 16:29.740
aren't you afraid
you won't be able to fall asleep?

16:30.370 --> 16:32.500
I'm not going to sleep tonight anyway.

16:34.140 --> 16:35.670
You're going to work again?

16:35.870 --> 16:37.070
I'm going to Qingshi.

16:38.570 --> 16:40.770
Are there still flights available now?

16:41.500 --> 16:42.560
I'm driving there.

16:43.490 --> 16:45.220
Driving at night is dangerous.

16:48.110 --> 16:50.310
I'm used to it. You should get some rest.

16:50.790 --> 16:51.990
For the next few days,

16:52.740 --> 16:54.140
stay home with Jin Qiang.

16:56.310 --> 16:57.190
A few days?

16:58.500 --> 17:00.300
You'll be gone for several days?

17:03.320 --> 17:03.950
Yes.

17:04.280 --> 17:05.609
I'm going to find a part.

17:05.700 --> 17:07.020
There's no one at the garage.

17:07.020 --> 17:08.950
You don't need to look for me there.

17:09.079 --> 17:10.010
I'm leaving now.

17:11.369 --> 17:13.630
I actually had some good news to tell you.

17:24.660 --> 17:25.859
I'm leaving at 10:30.

17:26.319 --> 17:28.040
What's the good news? Tell me.

17:32.850 --> 17:34.010
I plan to stay here

17:35.300 --> 17:36.760
and apply to a school here.

17:37.340 --> 17:38.590
Nana has already helped me sign up

17:38.590 --> 17:40.520
for a language foundation course.

17:46.060 --> 17:47.660
Have you thought it through?

17:48.800 --> 17:50.080
Do you want me to stay?

18:04.480 --> 18:06.280
Going to Canada with your mother

18:07.600 --> 18:10.200
would definitely be better
than staying here.

18:10.610 --> 18:12.410
You've seen what it's like here.

18:13.310 --> 18:15.110
It's not as good as you imagined.

18:15.700 --> 18:16.460
No.

18:16.670 --> 18:18.330
I think it's pretty good here.

18:19.460 --> 18:20.700
It's even

18:22.430 --> 18:23.950
better than I imagined.

18:25.480 --> 18:26.410
What do you mean?

18:32.590 --> 18:33.720
I'm not telling you.

18:35.790 --> 18:37.050
You have many secrets.

18:37.360 --> 18:38.490
Not as many as yours.

18:38.870 --> 18:40.470
You're the best at back talk.

18:48.740 --> 18:50.740
My business is nothing but trouble.

18:51.830 --> 18:53.490
It's better if you don't know.

18:57.220 --> 18:58.220
How about

18:58.950 --> 19:00.390
we exchange secrets?

19:01.150 --> 19:02.630
Tell me a bad secret,

19:02.910 --> 19:03.830
and I'll tell you a good...

19:03.830 --> 19:05.160
Let's talk another day.

19:05.470 --> 19:06.530
I really have to go.

19:10.110 --> 19:11.330
Do you have enough money?

19:11.330 --> 19:12.090
Yes.

19:23.240 --> 19:24.240
Eat meals on time.

19:25.230 --> 19:26.230
I'm a fussy eater.

19:28.400 --> 19:30.060
I don't like the food outside.

19:34.760 --> 19:35.630
Actually,

19:39.870 --> 19:41.870
you can ask Jin Qiang to cook for you.

19:42.260 --> 19:43.150
As you know,

19:43.330 --> 19:44.530
he's good at cooking.

19:47.630 --> 19:48.880
Come back soon.

19:54.760 --> 19:55.520
I'll try.

20:19.200 --> 20:20.730
Money isn't what I want.

21:22.020 --> 21:22.690
Dad,

21:26.860 --> 21:27.990
can you do me a favor?

21:30.510 --> 21:32.630
The environment and atmosphere here
are great,

21:32.630 --> 21:34.090
and the school is good too.

21:34.210 --> 21:35.840
I've already found a language class.

21:35.840 --> 21:37.600
It'll take about 3 or 4 months.

21:40.060 --> 21:42.060
Dad knows about it, and he agrees.

21:51.210 --> 21:52.580
Okay. I agree.

21:56.210 --> 21:57.210
Did you hear that?

21:57.380 --> 21:58.550
Dad said he agrees.

22:03.620 --> 22:06.020
I don't want to talk about Jin Zhao
with you.

22:07.510 --> 22:08.450
Alright, I'm tired.

22:08.450 --> 22:09.380
I'm going to bed.

22:12.540 --> 22:13.800
I'm going to sleep too.

22:15.150 --> 22:15.910
Dad,

22:17.110 --> 22:17.980
I'm hungry.

22:21.910 --> 22:23.370
What would you like to eat?

22:23.880 --> 22:26.190
Anything is fine. Make whatever you want.

22:26.190 --> 22:27.020
Wait here.

22:41.520 --> 22:46.490
♪ What would I do ♪

22:46.840 --> 22:49.240
♪ Would I write a song? ♪

22:49.600 --> 22:51.990
♪ No, I don't think so ♪

22:53.790 --> 22:56.110
♪ What would I do ♪

22:56.130 --> 22:58.870
♪ If I could fly up on the roof ♪

22:58.740 --> 22:59.910
See if it's okay to eat.

22:59.770 --> 23:01.120
♪ Would I rob a bank? ♪

23:01.920 --> 23:04.620
♪ Oh, I don't think so ♪

23:03.170 --> 23:04.860
This looks so delicious.

23:06.040 --> 23:08.370
♪ What would I do ♪

23:08.390 --> 23:11.620
♪ If I could turn invisible ♪

23:09.700 --> 23:10.300
Dad.

23:10.640 --> 23:12.640
You cook much better than Jin Zhao.

23:11.640 --> 23:14.120
♪ Would I drive my favorite car? ♪

23:12.980 --> 23:15.060
That kid doesn't compare to me.

23:14.150 --> 23:16.880
♪ No, I don't think so ♪

23:15.870 --> 23:18.220
You were much more handsome than him
when you were young.

23:17.670 --> 23:20.870
♪ I'd go to the restaurant ♪

23:18.390 --> 23:21.120
Stop flattering me.
Go to bed early after you eat.

23:21.370 --> 23:23.940
♪ Take all the fortune cookies ♪

23:22.700 --> 23:23.950
Dad, what about breakfast tomorrow?

23:23.950 --> 23:25.350
Don't disturb me tomorrow morning.

23:24.520 --> 23:26.940
♪ Read them one by one ♪

23:25.500 --> 23:26.700
I'm going to sleep in.

23:26.970 --> 23:28.160
♪ Till it says ♪

23:28.180 --> 23:30.040
♪ That I can be with you ♪

23:30.390 --> 23:32.940
♪ Sneak into the flower shop ♪

23:33.430 --> 23:36.440
♪ Watch how they make their bouquets ♪

23:36.600 --> 23:40.020
♪ So I could finally used ♪

23:38.630 --> 23:39.300
Jin Zhao.

23:40.160 --> 23:42.630
♪ The flowers I planted just for you ♪

23:40.680 --> 23:42.490
I've modified this connecting rod.

23:42.490 --> 23:43.620
See if it works.

23:48.070 --> 23:50.160
♪ Would you like that? ♪

23:51.040 --> 23:53.160
♪ Would you like that? ♪

23:52.700 --> 23:54.160
The material isn't right.

23:54.260 --> 23:55.460
This one is the closest.

23:55.460 --> 23:58.860
The one you're looking for
probably doesn't exist in Manshi.

24:00.320 --> 24:02.480
♪ Would you like that? ♪

24:01.810 --> 24:02.510
It's fine.

24:03.410 --> 24:05.480
♪ Would you like that? ♪

24:03.900 --> 24:04.600
Thank you.

24:05.350 --> 24:07.980
But if you insist on it,

24:08.190 --> 24:09.910
I suggest you craft one.

24:10.260 --> 24:11.530
With your current skills,

24:11.530 --> 24:13.400
you might be able to make it.

24:12.730 --> 24:14.810
♪ Would you like that? ♪

24:15.370 --> 24:15.980
Okay.

24:15.830 --> 24:17.910
♪ Would you like that? ♪

25:05.700 --> 25:06.590
Let's go.

25:43.020 --> 25:46.280
There are many blind curves
on the back hill. Safety first.

26:02.020 --> 26:03.280
Look at this black car.

26:03.630 --> 26:05.560
This is the first time I've seen it.

26:06.000 --> 26:07.330
It has great potential.

26:42.130 --> 26:42.990
Now is the time.

26:58.050 --> 27:00.050
There's water on the downhill road.

27:02.690 --> 27:03.980
Where did the water come from?

27:03.980 --> 27:05.500
Is this some kind of extra training mode?

27:05.500 --> 27:07.500
I've got rain tires on. Don't worry.

27:07.560 --> 27:09.150
Jin Zhao, your tires are the thinnest.

27:09.150 --> 27:09.990
Be careful.

27:10.260 --> 27:10.890
Thank you.

28:24.040 --> 28:24.840
Oh no.

28:25.570 --> 28:27.830
Jin Zhao's ranked in the top 10 in points.

29:05.870 --> 29:07.730
I'm ranked in the top 10 in points.

29:27.900 --> 29:28.510
Come here.

29:30.280 --> 29:32.520
This is my cousin's garage.

29:35.460 --> 29:36.940
It's so luxurious.

29:37.420 --> 29:38.820
Feel free to look around.

29:43.780 --> 29:46.110
Why does this place smell like a hospital?

29:47.790 --> 29:49.500
It must be the disinfectant.

29:49.820 --> 29:51.450
My cousin is a neat freak.

29:51.660 --> 29:52.870
He made the whole garage

29:52.870 --> 29:54.270
look like a sterile ward.

29:55.420 --> 29:56.280
And over there.

30:03.750 --> 30:04.670
This girl.

30:05.070 --> 30:06.070
Why is she here?

30:09.500 --> 30:11.630
This is a 1999 GTR34.

30:11.930 --> 30:13.410
I only saw it in movies.

30:13.750 --> 30:16.180
Mu, you know quite a lot.

30:17.200 --> 30:18.310
It's nothing special.

30:18.310 --> 30:20.870
My cousin treasures these cars so much.

30:20.990 --> 30:23.520
Outsiders aren't even
allowed to touch them.

30:24.280 --> 30:25.040
But you

30:25.260 --> 30:26.790
can feel free to touch them.

30:27.300 --> 30:27.980
Really?

30:28.070 --> 30:28.700
Yes.

30:30.300 --> 30:32.170
Then I won't hold back.

30:36.160 --> 30:37.920
This car's pedal is so tiny

30:38.110 --> 30:39.260
and delicate.

30:40.460 --> 30:42.260
My cousin must have modified it.

30:42.270 --> 30:44.420
My cousin is extremely meticulous.

30:44.660 --> 30:46.670
He's a perfectionist
when it comes to modifying cars.

30:46.670 --> 30:49.280
He's super demanding.

30:52.980 --> 30:54.040
I'll take the call.

30:57.630 --> 31:00.150
One really shouldn't talk
behind people's backs.

31:00.150 --> 31:01.480
It's my cousin calling.

31:03.700 --> 31:04.390
Sui.

31:04.660 --> 31:05.460
Where are you?

31:07.350 --> 31:10.260
I'm grocery shopping with my mom.

31:10.700 --> 31:11.590
Um, uh...

31:11.610 --> 31:12.750
How much is half a kilo of cilantro?

31:12.750 --> 31:14.220
Do you still want

31:14.630 --> 31:16.360
the guitar you liked last time?

31:16.870 --> 31:18.020
You're giving it to me?

31:18.020 --> 31:19.740
Meet me within 5 minutes,

31:20.060 --> 31:21.390
and the guitar is yours.

31:21.400 --> 31:22.570
5 minutes?

31:23.740 --> 31:25.200
Okay, I'll be right there.

31:25.210 --> 31:25.930
Wait for me.

31:26.540 --> 31:27.980
Mu, I'm going to get a guitar.

31:27.980 --> 31:28.670
I'll be right back.

31:28.670 --> 31:29.220
Wait for me.

31:29.220 --> 31:30.620
Feel free to look around.

31:44.760 --> 31:45.560
Nana?

31:47.510 --> 31:48.270
Nana?

31:48.830 --> 31:49.630
Nana?

31:51.000 --> 31:51.850
Nana?

31:59.190 --> 31:59.840
Na...

32:02.030 --> 32:02.890
It's you again.

32:03.150 --> 32:04.680
Which racing team sent you?

32:05.010 --> 32:06.170
What racing team?

32:07.830 --> 32:09.620
You used Nana to get close to me.

32:10.540 --> 32:11.970
Don't be so full of yourself.

32:11.970 --> 32:13.820
What's in it for me?

32:14.720 --> 32:16.920
You should be answering my questions,

32:17.910 --> 32:19.540
not asking me your own.

32:20.870 --> 32:22.130
What if I don't answer?

32:22.910 --> 32:24.190
Then you're

32:25.150 --> 32:26.480
not leaving here today.

32:31.820 --> 32:34.060
What's your reason for taking photos here?

32:34.060 --> 32:35.670
Tell me. I want to know.

32:36.800 --> 32:38.060
I was just curious,

32:38.190 --> 32:40.320
so Nana brought me here to look around.

32:43.260 --> 32:44.790
But after looking around,

32:45.700 --> 32:48.500
I'm not that impressed.
There's nothing special.

32:49.760 --> 32:50.880
Then tell me,

32:51.390 --> 32:52.540
what is special?

32:54.030 --> 32:54.980
My friend

32:55.340 --> 32:57.020
has a Wankel engine.

32:57.090 --> 32:58.490
It's really impressive.

32:59.220 --> 33:00.590
A Wankel engine?

33:01.590 --> 33:02.720
Your friend has one?

33:03.240 --> 33:03.870
Yes.

33:06.000 --> 33:07.640
Anyway, it's none of your business.

33:07.640 --> 33:09.170
Let me out. I want to go home.

33:15.780 --> 33:16.590
Get in.

33:17.730 --> 33:18.700
Where are we going?

33:18.700 --> 33:19.740
I'll take you out.

33:21.310 --> 33:22.110
Where's Nana?

33:22.780 --> 33:23.540
She's fine.

33:24.460 --> 33:25.950
Don't you like this car?

33:26.290 --> 33:27.620
I'll take you for a spin.

33:40.400 --> 33:42.530
What did you take pictures of just now?

33:43.980 --> 33:44.940
What pictures?

33:47.250 --> 33:48.910
I have surveillance cameras.

33:52.750 --> 33:53.660
The pedal.

33:54.700 --> 33:55.830
It looks tiny,

33:56.050 --> 33:57.770
light, and elegant.

34:01.740 --> 34:03.350
A light clutch is easy to operate.

34:03.350 --> 34:05.300
Faster coupling reduces time loss.

34:05.300 --> 34:07.390
This, in turn,
leads to better performance.

34:07.390 --> 34:09.230
It's a simple principle.

34:11.770 --> 34:13.480
I also drove a car a few days ago.

34:13.480 --> 34:16.810
Its clutch was huge and stiff.
It was really hard to control.

34:19.230 --> 34:20.790
Was it a pickup truck?

34:21.460 --> 34:22.320
How do you know?

34:22.750 --> 34:25.350
The stiff clutch is caused by
its hard springs.

34:25.460 --> 34:27.500
It enables a quick connection

34:27.830 --> 34:30.909
between the engine and transmission
when shifting.

34:31.670 --> 34:34.270
Locally, only pickup enthusiasts

34:34.540 --> 34:36.020
use hard springs.

34:36.480 --> 34:38.480
Stomping on it to shift is too rude.

34:40.500 --> 34:41.760
You shift quickly too,

34:41.870 --> 34:43.469
but your clutch isn't stiff.

34:44.010 --> 34:47.139
Every car has its own performance balance.

34:47.389 --> 34:48.250
How to modify it

34:48.449 --> 34:50.449
depends on the owner's preference.

34:50.540 --> 34:52.100
That's the meaning for us car enthusiasts.

34:52.100 --> 34:53.230
The same car model

34:53.580 --> 34:55.060
holds endless possibilities.

34:55.060 --> 34:55.750
Besides,

34:55.909 --> 34:57.370
elegance and performance

34:58.170 --> 34:59.490
aren't mutually exclusive.

34:59.490 --> 35:00.260
But

35:01.130 --> 35:02.330
I hate rudeness.

35:16.170 --> 35:17.630
I look better than the car?

35:18.430 --> 35:20.180
No. Don't get the wrong idea.

35:20.660 --> 35:22.580
It's just that the way you drive

35:22.600 --> 35:23.860
reminds me of someone.

35:23.930 --> 35:24.970
Your friend

35:25.960 --> 35:28.440
with a Wankel engine?

35:29.190 --> 35:29.870
Yes.

35:31.140 --> 35:32.380
You both seem

35:32.830 --> 35:33.870
very relaxed.

35:38.140 --> 35:39.140
Where do you live?

35:39.390 --> 35:40.430
I'll drive you home.

35:40.430 --> 35:41.200
No need.

35:41.530 --> 35:43.150
Just drop me off at the service area.

35:43.150 --> 35:44.150
I'll take a taxi.

35:47.310 --> 35:48.970
Until you tell me the address,

35:49.790 --> 35:51.230
I'm not letting you out.

36:24.350 --> 36:26.660
You're the first person
who dared to slam my car door.

36:26.660 --> 36:28.230
If you dare to make me angry again,

36:28.230 --> 36:29.250
I might become the first person

36:29.250 --> 36:30.330
to smash your car.

36:39.850 --> 36:40.520
Okay.

36:40.990 --> 36:42.990
I'll give you that chance next time.

36:43.750 --> 36:44.910
Is this

36:45.340 --> 36:47.100
a Sichuan restaurant?

36:47.810 --> 36:49.340
I really like Chinese food.

36:49.990 --> 36:50.840
Sorry.

36:51.270 --> 36:52.640
They only sell dumplings here,

36:52.640 --> 36:53.660
and it's just that one type

36:53.660 --> 36:56.460
with extremely salty
pickled vegetable filling.

37:07.940 --> 37:08.830
Zhao.

37:09.440 --> 37:11.130
I have something to tell you.

37:14.260 --> 37:15.130
Jin Qiang's

37:15.500 --> 37:18.100
eldest daughter seems to be
in a relationship.

37:19.270 --> 37:20.020
Jiang Mu?

37:20.770 --> 37:22.890
Yes, I saw it with my own eyes.

37:23.310 --> 37:24.060
I hope

37:24.260 --> 37:25.720
nothing goes wrong. Otherwise,

37:25.720 --> 37:27.570
how would I explain it to her mother?

37:27.570 --> 37:28.700
You're close to her.

37:28.930 --> 37:29.660
How about

37:29.890 --> 37:31.000
you talk to her

37:31.230 --> 37:32.870
and find out what happened?

37:33.370 --> 37:34.390
What did you see?

37:34.590 --> 37:35.630
A man

37:35.680 --> 37:37.470
just drove her back in a sports car.

37:37.470 --> 37:38.870
And he's still there,

37:39.050 --> 37:40.970
talking nonstop.

37:42.600 --> 37:43.240
Are you sure?

37:43.240 --> 37:44.200
Of course.

37:44.580 --> 37:45.750
I have sharp eyes.

37:47.240 --> 37:47.910
I knew.

37:48.970 --> 37:50.850
Zhao, listen to me.

37:50.900 --> 37:53.310
Have a good talk with her.

37:53.790 --> 37:56.060
This girl seems quite stubborn.

37:56.490 --> 37:58.320
Otherwise, she wouldn't have come here

37:58.320 --> 37:59.950
instead of going abroad
like her mother wanted.

37:59.950 --> 38:01.700
When you talk to her,

38:01.880 --> 38:03.800
be careful about your approach.

38:06.190 --> 38:06.870
Okay.

38:07.230 --> 38:08.190
I'll talk to her.

38:58.730 --> 38:59.880
You seem

39:00.460 --> 39:02.190
very familiar with this place.

39:02.870 --> 39:04.420
What do you usually do here?

39:10.000 --> 39:12.130
What nonsense are you thinking about?

39:14.230 --> 39:16.670
No. I was just asking.

39:41.840 --> 39:43.370
Have you ever thought about

39:44.830 --> 39:47.590
what kind of person you'd like to marry
in the future?

39:47.590 --> 39:48.430
No, I haven't.

39:54.230 --> 39:55.360
Why did you ask this?

39:57.630 --> 39:58.630
I was just asking.

40:05.060 --> 40:06.270
When I was in school,

40:07.900 --> 40:08.980
a guy in my class

40:10.620 --> 40:12.050
chased a girl from another class

40:12.050 --> 40:13.050
pretty actively.

40:14.010 --> 40:16.720
He brought her food in the morning
and drinks in the afternoon.

40:16.720 --> 40:18.120
He also gave her gifts constantly.

40:18.120 --> 40:19.650
He was such a smooth talker.

40:19.720 --> 40:21.780
He had her wrapped around his finger.

40:22.720 --> 40:23.850
But behind her back,

40:24.490 --> 40:26.020
he talked to us about

40:26.040 --> 40:27.640
things too vulgar to repeat.

40:28.270 --> 40:30.670
He even shared intimate details about them

40:31.200 --> 40:32.730
as something to brag about.

40:34.640 --> 40:35.760
Guess what happened next.

40:35.760 --> 40:36.620
What happened?

40:37.150 --> 40:38.940
The girl's grades dropped off.

40:39.570 --> 40:41.900
Her family came to school
and made a scene.

40:42.580 --> 40:43.980
The boy broke up with her.

40:45.040 --> 40:46.640
The girl couldn't accept it.

40:46.710 --> 40:47.510
She took pills

40:48.150 --> 40:49.480
and attempted suicide.

40:50.140 --> 40:51.140
What do you think?

40:51.230 --> 40:53.270
Well, but...

40:53.870 --> 40:56.060
There was no need to attempt suicide.

41:04.790 --> 41:06.350
At your age,

41:07.570 --> 41:09.100
a boy's attraction to a girl

41:09.350 --> 41:11.080
is mostly just a passing fancy.

41:11.100 --> 41:12.020
To them,

41:12.670 --> 41:14.100
getting a pretty girl

41:14.290 --> 41:15.530
is just about having a trophy

41:15.530 --> 41:16.340
to show off.

41:16.640 --> 41:18.170
They lack responsibility.

41:18.460 --> 41:19.540
Not necessarily.

41:19.990 --> 41:22.050
There was a couple in my class before.

41:22.540 --> 41:24.260
Later, they were both admitted to NUAA.

41:24.260 --> 41:25.860
They're still together now.

41:32.710 --> 41:35.400
♪ Waiting, still waiting ♪

41:35.550 --> 41:38.880
♪ You, weaving through my heart ♪

41:39.460 --> 41:43.220
♪ My thoughts of you will never cease ♪

41:43.330 --> 41:47.320
♪ Waiting for your ship to arrive ♪

41:47.550 --> 41:51.000
♪ I'm still waiting, still waiting ♪

41:51.030 --> 41:54.320
♪ You, chasing after the moon ♪

41:54.860 --> 41:57.250
♪ Scattered across the sky ♪

41:57.310 --> 41:58.660
But most boys

41:57.430 --> 42:00.820
♪ And me, here by your side ♪

41:59.140 --> 42:00.940
at this age aren't mature enough

42:01.950 --> 42:02.710
to shoulder

42:02.710 --> 42:04.350
responsibility.

42:09.230 --> 42:10.100
What about you?

42:12.080 --> 42:13.600
Are you that kind of boy?

42:19.180 --> 42:22.070
♪ Stars are twinkling in the sky ♪

42:22.460 --> 42:25.430
♪ Like your twinkling eyes ♪

42:25.680 --> 42:28.460
♪ Telling me ♪

42:29.750 --> 42:32.320
♪ A beautiful dream from afar ♪

42:34.350 --> 42:37.570
♪ Night is painted with neon lights ♪

42:38.080 --> 42:41.160
♪ The street is gentle and busy ♪

42:38.180 --> 42:39.010
Hold me.

42:41.390 --> 42:45.230
♪ I paused and wandered far ♪

42:45.620 --> 42:49.270
♪ You're like a breeze ♪

42:50.060 --> 42:52.570
♪ I watch you leave ♪

42:53.390 --> 42:56.820
♪ I wish I could hug you from the back ♪

42:56.940 --> 42:58.310
The person you meet won't be me.

42:57.290 --> 43:00.360
♪ Lingering in the air ♪

43:00.460 --> 43:01.710
How do you know the person I meet

43:00.670 --> 43:03.820
♪ Your breath is everywhere ♪

43:01.710 --> 43:02.580
can't be you?

43:05.420 --> 43:08.570
♪ Waiting, still waiting ♪

43:05.620 --> 43:06.660
I mean,

43:07.360 --> 43:08.480
someone like you.

43:08.880 --> 43:11.820
♪ You, weaving through my heart ♪

43:12.290 --> 43:16.070
♪ My thoughts of you will never cease ♪

43:16.100 --> 43:20.790
♪ Waiting for your ship to arrive ♪

43:20.900 --> 43:23.580
♪ Waiting, still waiting ♪

43:23.580 --> 43:24.670
Are you nearsighted?

43:24.250 --> 43:26.820
♪ You, weaving through my heart ♪

43:25.490 --> 43:26.220
Hold me.

43:26.760 --> 43:27.600
About -1.00.

43:27.630 --> 43:31.330
♪ My thoughts of you will never cease ♪

43:28.780 --> 43:30.580
Why aren't you wearing glasses?

43:30.660 --> 43:31.660
I wore them yesterday.

43:31.480 --> 43:35.080
♪ Waiting for your ship to arrive ♪

43:32.320 --> 43:33.310
I don't like them.

43:33.310 --> 43:34.510
They don't look good.

43:34.660 --> 43:35.790
You should wear them.

43:35.790 --> 43:38.830
♪ I'm still waiting, still waiting ♪

43:36.470 --> 43:37.110
No.

43:39.170 --> 43:40.290
If you take this kind of path again,

43:39.330 --> 43:42.780
♪ You, chasing after the moon ♪

43:41.130 --> 43:42.260
no one will hold you.

43:43.510 --> 43:45.780
♪ Scattered across the sky ♪

43:46.140 --> 43:49.280
♪ And me, here by your side ♪

43:49.840 --> 43:54.030
♪ No matter clear or rainy night ♪

43:51.190 --> 43:54.190
I won't take this kind of path
with anyone else either.

43:58.550 --> 44:05.880
♪ I'll light it up, for you ♪

44:06.430 --> 44:08.560
[Speeding Auto House]

44:10.180 --> 44:11.060
We're back.

44:12.940 --> 44:13.830
You're back.

44:16.060 --> 44:17.790
I was wondering where you went.

44:17.810 --> 44:19.420
You went to pick up this pretty lady.

44:19.420 --> 44:21.350
I heard you're going to study here.

44:22.840 --> 44:24.230
I signed up
for a language foundation course.

44:24.230 --> 44:25.560
It'll take 3 or 4 months.

44:25.830 --> 44:27.960
I plan to take an exam after I finish it.

44:28.160 --> 44:29.470
That's great.

44:30.120 --> 44:32.120
So you'll be living here from now on?

44:36.310 --> 44:37.310
Not necessarily.

44:37.460 --> 44:38.920
I might go back to Nanjing.

44:39.060 --> 44:40.180
After all, that's where Jin Zhao and I

44:40.180 --> 44:41.460
grew up together.

44:44.840 --> 44:45.640
Jin Zhao?

44:47.270 --> 44:48.670
Now you call him Jin Zhao?

44:48.920 --> 44:50.450
You don't call him Brother?

44:51.070 --> 44:51.760
Yes.

44:52.530 --> 44:53.820
That's what I call him now.

44:53.820 --> 44:54.660
Why?

44:55.390 --> 44:56.100
No...

44:56.380 --> 44:58.240
Why do you have so many questions?

45:02.540 --> 45:03.600
Did you come alone?

45:04.540 --> 45:05.270
No.

45:05.630 --> 45:06.830
Guess who I came with.

45:09.710 --> 45:10.770
You must be hungry.

45:11.430 --> 45:12.960
You can study after eating.

45:13.420 --> 45:14.620
I'll go wash my hands.

45:16.990 --> 45:18.250
She's living here now?

45:23.340 --> 45:24.050
Where?

45:31.670 --> 45:32.790
Let's talk about it later.
